# Summary
Amplitude Activation's Recommendations feature uses AutoML to determine which items are most likely to drive users toward a predictive goal, clustering users based on properties and behaviors to generate personalized item rankings that update hourly, best suited for user-based personalization in ecommerce, marketplace, and B2C companies.

